  "slug": "equivalent-additions",
  "title": "Equivalent Additions",
  "description": "An addon for ProjectE that adds features you miss so much!",
  "body": "<p><strong>This mod requires&nbsp;<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/hammer-lib\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://curseforge.zeith.org/api/v2/logo?id=247401\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />&nbsp;HammerLib</a>.</strong></p>\n\n<p>Welcome! This mod expands ProjectE with some cool, and OP items and blocks!</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Currently, it adds (The list is VERY outdated!):</p>\n<ul>\n<li>EMC Conduits\n<ul>\n<li><img src=\"https://tehenopengin.github.io/mod-icons/assets/equivadditions/conduit_mk1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />MK1 -&nbsp; 256 EMC/tick</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://tehenopengin.github.io/mod-icons/assets/equivadditions/conduit_mk2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />MK2 -&nbsp; 1 024 EMC/tick</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://tehenopengin.github.io/mod-icons/assets/equivadditions/conduit_mk3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />MK3 -&nbsp; 4 096 EMC/tick</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://tehenopengin.github.io/mod-icons/assets/equivadditions/conduit_mk4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />MK4 -&nbsp; 16 384 EMC/tick</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://tehenopengin.github.io/mod-icons/assets/equivadditions/zeitheron_fuel_block.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />&nbsp;Zeitheron Fuel Block</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://tehenopengin.github.io/mod-icons/assets/equivadditions/blue_matter_block.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />&nbsp;Blue Matter Block</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://tehenopengin.github.io/mod-icons/assets/equivadditions/collector_mk4.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />&nbsp;Energy Collector MK4</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://tehenopengin.github.io/mod-icons/assets/equivadditions/relay_mk4.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />&nbsp;Anti-Matter Relay MK4</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://tehenopengin.github.io/mod-icons/assets/equivadditions/blue_matter.gif\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />&nbsp;Blue Matter</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://tehenopengin.github.io/mod-icons/assets/equivadditions/zeitheron_fuel.gif\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />&nbsp;Zeitheron Fuel</li>\n<li><img src=\"https://tehenopengin.github.io/mod-icons/assets/equivadditions/emc_proxy.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />&nbsp;EMC Proxy - Absorbs all incoming EMC from collectors, relays, and conduits. Transfers EMC to the owner's transmutation tablet when the owner is online.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">As of now, ideas are welcome!</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LuJJMv1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"698\" height=\"1\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Permissions:</strong></p>\n<ul style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You&nbsp;can use this mod in your modpack.</strong></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You are not allowed to re-publish this mod to other sites without providing a Modrinth/CurseForge download link and my permission (PM to <a href=\"https://me.zeith.gay/\"><img src=\"https://dccg.herokuapp.com/discord/fetchAvatar/376091478142746625\" alt=\"\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />&nbsp;Zeitheron</a>, or via Discord)</strong></li>\n<li style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>You are not allowed to include this (or any other mods of the DragonForge team) in your own mod. Building add-ons, however, is allowed, but a friendly PM would be good.</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>The only supported version of Minecraft is the latest one that this mod exists for. DO NOT ASK TO DOWNGRADE!</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"js-qwynlraxz\" href=\"https://ds.zeith.org/dev\"><img src=\"https://ds.zeith.org/cards/dev.png\" width=\"510\" height=\"170\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Want to discuss anything? Need help with APIs?</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Join the discord server and follow Zeitheron on <a href=\"http://bit.ly/ZeithTwitter\"><img src=\"https://abs.twimg.com/favicons/twitter.ico\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />Twitter</a>!</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>If you would like to support my work, you can become a patron via <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/zeitheron\"><img src=\"https://c5.patreon.com/external/favicon/favicon-32x32.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" />&nbsp;Patreon</a>.&nbsp;<img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/pix.iemoji.com/twit33/0744.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"33\" height=\"33\" /></strong></p>",
